test_Withdraw_UTXOReservationIsGlobalNot.details: F-002: Observes whether withdraw(txId, outputId) reservation is global (keyed only by UTXO)       or caller-bound. Two distinct addresses attempt the same (txId, outputId); we assert       the second attempt reverts with "UTXO already used" regardless of caller.
